Discover the perfect stay with the Global Hotel Card, powered by Expedia. Enjoy the convenience of booking your hotel or vacation rental from a vast selection of accommodations available online. Whether you're planning a relaxing getaway or a business trip, use up to 4 (four) Gift Cards per booking to cover the cost. Please note that the Global Hotel Card can only be redeemed online atwww.globalhotelcard.comand cannot be used directly at the hotel or onExpedia.com.
